 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n彩雀大極都係咁上下，有雀通常唔養貓，貓既口水會令雀死</blockquote><br />\n鸚鵡三個月就生定個骨架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能遲啲會肥小小同毛長小小 唔會大得去邊<br />\n你養之前都無乜做過功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因爲唔係我買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我呀妹突然帶番黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"263cf44d7ce7d04b983151deade3d71f6e3bec28","tid":194023,"uid":39177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T05:56:35.000Z","msg":"彩鳳唔識講野,別期望太高,學識點養後可以買隻bb陪佢"},{"pid":"f6c54f2de113e136ecdcfe804c00cb66bfd8fc90","tid":194023,"uid":5220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:10:15.000Z","msg":"唔好養貓啊<br />\n貓殺雀係天性黎<br />\n我老豆個同事又係養貓養雀<br />\n一直都相安無事<br />\n但有一日隻貓無啦啦發癲打死隻雀<br />\n個同事最後打撚死埋隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b882a7b19f9aa8f00c1b12dff5a160665bede45d","tid":194023,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T09:16:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好養貓啊<br />\n貓殺雀係天性黎<br />\n我老豆個同事又係養貓養雀<br />\n一直都相安無事<br />\n但有一日隻貓無啦啦發癲打死隻雀<br />\n個同事最後打撚死埋隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />報警"},{"pid":"60e30fb0853ba981aa5384bed6aa5381635e46e6","tid":194023,"uid":98696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T05:11:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好養貓啊<br />\n貓殺雀係天性黎<br />\n我老豆個同事又係養貓養雀<br />\n一直都相安無事<br />\n但有一日隻貓無啦啦發癲打死隻雀<br />\n個同事最後打撚死埋隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54def8afa7de47df0d6fc8b3780314bee3f35278","tid":194023,"uid":76488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T05:12: